5 PROVIDE THE DATE OF DEATH, DEATH CERTIFICATE STATE AND
6 FILE/REGISTRATION NUMBER HERE. IF THE BENEFICIARY OR BENEFICIARIES DIED
7 PRIOR TO THE TRANSFEROR, THEIR INTEREST IN THE PROPERTY HAS LAPSED.
