HOUSE BILL 738 31
1 OR
2 OPTION TWO:
3 ____ AT LEAST ONE OF THE BENEFICIARIES INHERITING THE SUBJECT PROPERTY
4 UNDER THE DEED REFERENCED IN THIS NOTIFICATION LIVES AT THIS PROPERTY AS
5 THEIR PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE.
6 IF YOU SELECTED OPTION TWO AND YOU ARE THE BENEFICIARY OCCUPYING THE
7 PROPERTY, PLEASE COMPLETE THE FOLLOWING:
8 I, ______________________ (PRINT NAME), DO HEREBY CERTIFY AND AFFIRM UNDER
9 THE PENALTIES OF PERJURY THAT I CURRENTLY LIVE AT AND WILL CONTINUE TO
10 LIVE AT THE ABOVE–REFERENCED PROPERTY, FOLLOWING THE RECORDING OF
11 THIS NOTIFICATION. I SHALL OCCUPY THE PROPERTY AS MY PRINCIPAL RESIDENCE
12 FOR AT LEAST 7 OF THE NEXT 12 MONTHS.
